# MovieList — theme and component styling

## Cinematic Curator

- Colours follow the **Cinematic Curator** palette — centralize in **`src/theme/colors.ts`** (and related theme files). Do not scatter one-off hex values in components.

## Typography

- Use **`src/theme/typography.ts`** (and font loading via theme) for **Manrope** / **Inter** tokens — font sizes, weights, line heights from tokens.

## Spacing and layout

- Spacing **only** from **`src/theme/spacing.ts`**.
- **Portrait content cards:** **`radiusCardOuter`** / **`radiusCardInner`** and **`contentCard.aspectRatio`** (**2:3**) — reference tokens only; no raw radii or aspect literals in components.
- **No 1px** decorative layout borders. **No pure `#FFFFFF`** for text — use semantic text colours from theme.

## Implementation

- **`StyleSheet.create`** only. No NativeWind, Styled Components, or CSS-in-JS.
